      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Method"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Heat the {{rapeseed-oil}} in a large frying pan over medium heat. Add the {{sausages-pork}}. Cook for 15 minutes, turning every 3 minutes, until evenly bronzed all over."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Heat the grill to high. Spread the {{mushrooms-chestnut}} and halved {{tomato}} on a baking tray. Drizzle with a teaspoon of oil and season. Grill for 8 minutes until the mushrooms release their liquid and the tomatoes blister."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Push the sausages to one side of the frying pan. Lay the {{back-bacon}} and {{black-pudding}} slices in the gap. Cook for 3 minutes a side. The bacon fat crisps and the pudding's surface darkens."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Tip the {{baked-beans}} into a small saucepan over low heat and warm gently, stirring now and then. Drop the {{bread}} into the toaster."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Heat a teaspoon of oil in a small frying pan over medium heat. Crack the {{eggs}} into the pan. Cook for 2 minutes, spooning hot oil over the whites to set the tops without flipping. The yolks stay runny."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Butter the hot toast with {{salted-butter}}. Divide everything between two warm plates: sausages, bacon, black pudding, tomatoes, mushrooms, a pool of beans, the egg on top. Toast on the side. Eat straight away: the plate cools fast."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "troubleshooter",
