          "intro": null,
          "items": [
            {
              "fix": "Start sausages first. Bacon, mushrooms, tomatoes in the second wave. Eggs and toast in the last 2 minutes.",
              "cause": "Sequencing off; everything finished separately.",
              "symptom": "Half the plate cold by the time the rest is ready"
            },
            {
              "fix": "Medium heat; spoon hot oil over to set the whites. Pull at 2 minutes.",
              "cause": "Pan too hot.",
              "symptom": "Eggs overcooked"
            },
            {
              "fix": "Buy thick-cut back bacon; cook over medium heat.",
              "cause": "Too thin, or cooked too high.",
              "symptom": "Bacon shrivelled"
            },
            {
              "fix": "Halve across the equator, not pole to pole. Eight minutes under the grill is the minimum.",
              "cause": "Grill too close, or tomatoes too thick.",
              "symptom": "Tomatoes raw inside"
            },
            {
              "fix": "Spread in a single layer. The water has to escape.",
              "cause": "Crowded on the tray.",
              "symptom": "Mushrooms slimy"
            }
          ],
          "heading": "Common problems"
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Where this dish lives"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "The full English is the British weekend breakfast, the transport-cafe midweek lunch, and the seaside hotel order at 11 a.m. Each region claims its own version: the full Scottish adds tattie scones and haggis; the Ulster fry brings soda farls; the full Welsh swaps in laverbread; the West Country adds hog's pudding. The plate above is the southern English baseline. A pot of strong tea is the only correct drink."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
